OL,3,CUnder-16s social media ban backed by
OL,4,CLords
OL,6,FA ban on social media for under-16s
OL,7,Fhas been backed by the House of Lords,
OL,8,Ffollowing growing calls from
OL,9,Fcampaigners including actor Hugh Grant.
OL,11,FSupporters of the Australian-style ban
OL,12,Fhave argued parents are in "an
OL,13,Fimpossible position" with regard to
OL,14,Fthe online harms their children are
OL,15,Fbeing exposed to.
