OL,6,FTechnology Secretary Liz Kendall
OL,7,Fannounced a three-month consultation
OL,8,Fthis week, which will consider the
OL,9,Fadvantages and disadvantages of a ban,
OL,10,Fas well as possible overnight curfews
OL,11,Fand actions to prevent "doom-
OL,12,Fscrolling", reporting back in the
OL,13,Fsummer.
OL,15,FHowever, former schools minister Lord
OL,16,FNash said the consultation simply
OL,17,Frepresents more delay.
