OL,3,CUnder-16s social media ban backed by
OL,4,CLords
OL,6,FTikTok, Instagram, Facebook, X,
OL,7,FSnapchat, YouTube, Kick, Twitch,
OL,8,FThreads, and Reddit have all been
OL,9,Fimpacted by the changes after
OL,10,FAustralian officials deemed the sites
OL,11,Fharmful to young people.
OL,13,FCampaigners for a UK ban have argued
OL,14,Fsocial media is fuelling catastrophic
OL,15,Fharm to children's health and driving
OL,16,Fradicalisation and crime, in addition
OL,17,Fto an epidemic of mental illness.
